exports[`Snapshot — every dialect with tool change and WCS > Fanuc 4-axis with tool T2, WCS G56, RPM 9000 1`] = `
"(Comprehensive Snapshot Mill — snapshot-comprehensive)
(4-AXIS A-ROTARY G-CODE — FANUC DIALECT)
(---------------------------------------------------------------------------)
(UNVERIFIED G-CODE — VERIFY EVERY LINE AGAINST YOUR FANUC CONTROLLER MANUAL)
(BEFORE RUNNING ON A MACHINE. OUTPUT IS NOT GUARANTEED SAFE FOR ANY MACHINE.)
(---------------------------------------------------------------------------)
(CRITICAL 4TH AXIS CHECKS BEFORE RUNNING:)
(1 — CONFIRM THE ROTARY TABLE OR CHUCK IS FIRMLY CLAMPED TO THE MACHINE TABLE.)
(2 — CONFIRM THE WORKPIECE IS CENTRED ON THE ROTARY AXIS — OFF-CENTRE)
(    STOCK CAUSES GOUGING AND CRASHES.)
(3 — CONFIRM CYLINDER DIAMETER MATCHES THE VALUE USED TO GENERATE TOOLPATHS.)
(4 — SET A-AXIS WCS ZERO — USUALLY THE LEFT FACE OF THE CYLINDER AT A=0 DEG.)
(5 — AIR-CUT WITH SPINDLE OFF AT 10 PCT FEED OVERRIDE BEFORE A REAL CUT.)
(6 — CONFIRM YOUR FANUC CONTROL SUPPORTS A-AXIS COMMANDS AND THAT THE)
(    ROTARY AXIS IS PROPERLY CONFIGURED IN PARAMETERS.)
(---------------------------------------------------------------------------)
(RETRACT ORDER: LIFT Z TO SAFE CLEARANCE BEFORE COMMANDING LARGE A MOVES.)
(BEFORE PRODUCTION: DRY RUN — SPINDLE OFF, Z HIGH, FEED REDUCED.)
(SEE DOCS/MACHINES.MD — SAFE Z, WCS, UNITS, SPINDLE M-CODES.)
(---------------------------------------------------------------------------)
(WORK AREA MM: 300 X 200 X 100)
(A-AXIS RANGE: 360 DEG — VERIFY AGAINST MACHINE TRAVEL LIMITS)
G21              (METRIC — MUST MATCH CONTROLLER SETTING)
G90                    (ABSOLUTE DISTANCE MODE — X Y Z A ALL ABSOLUTE)
G17                    (XY PLANE FOR G2/G3 ARCS)
G40 G49 G80           (CANCEL CUTTER COMP, TOOL LENGTH COMP, CANNED CYCLES)
(ACTIVE WORK OFFSET — VERIFY FIXTURE ZERO MATCHES G54-G59 SELECTION)
G56
(OPERATION: Comprehensive Dialect Test)
(SAFE RETRACT — LIFT Z BEFORE ANY A-AXIS ROTATION TO AVOID COLLISIONS)
G0 Z100
(SPINDLE ON — CONFIRM S VALUE MATCHES YOUR TOOL AND MATERIAL)
M3 S9000
(--- 4-AXIS TOOLPATH MOVES BEGIN — X Y Z A WORDS ---)
G0 X0 Y0 Z20 A0
G1 X10 Z-2.000 A0 F600
G1 X10 Z-2.000 A90 F400
G1 X10 Z-2.000 A180 F400
G1 X10 Z-2.000 A270 F400
G0 Z20 A0
(--- END TOOLPATH ---)
(SPINDLE OFF)
M5
(SAFE RETRACT AND RETURN TO REFERENCE POSITION)
G91 G28 Z0            (RETURN Z TO REFERENCE POINT — INCREMENTAL MODE)
G91 G28 X0 Y0         (RETURN X Y TO HOME POSITION)
G90                    (RESTORE ABSOLUTE MODE)
G0 A0                 (RETURN A-AXIS TO ZERO)
M30                   (PROGRAM END AND REWIND)
"
`;

